room_title: Escape room "Bank Heist" by Escape Room Alexandria in Alexandria (MN)
room_description:
You’re a successful safe-cracker and your team has prepared for today’s challenge – attempting a heist at Andes Tower Bank.
Your recon team has just completed phase one of the heist – ensuring the building is empty and gaining access to the bank manager’s office, where the door to the vault awaits. Since this heist is vault will be so difficult to crack, they have discreetly hidden clues, tools and hints around the office which you will need to complete your job as safe-cracker.
